- Compile players list
- Set search settings
- Open Web App on your browser (preferably Italia web app)
- Active full screen mode using the top right button
- Go to the market page
- Press Ctrl + S to start research
- Don't touch anything while program is working
- To stop searching press Ctrl + S again
